{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"3d6aff5f-3913-46d3-a0b5-702d66c2e551","content":"\n\nYou can filter by class name using the `--filter` option:\n\n```bash\ndotnet test --filter \"FullyQualifiedName~ReportExporterTests\"\n```\n\nOr using the shorter `ClassName` filter:\n\n```bash\ndotnet test --filter \"ClassName=ReportExporterTests\"\n```\n\nIf the class is in a namespace, you may need to fully qualify it:\n\n```bash\ndotnet test --filter \"FullyQualifiedName~Namespace.ReportExporterTests\"\n```","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"d656b0dd-7547-4f9b-8180-4393ff0f3703","outputTokens":125,"requestId":"4816:2AD648:80C892:943A00:69FBE941"},"id":"7a38e00d-40b4-49d2-9e57-6cca4cb56e1b","timestamp":"2026-05-07T01:22:26.098Z","parentId":"15fd7425-f29f-48e9-88a2-d9615fd09f29"}
